{"tid":1732210,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"理大校長滕錦光錄影發言　籲示威者自首　稱曾想赴現場但警指不適合","createTime":"2019-11-18T00:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T00:50:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48a16881f819d2fe0d66d8663f29f1326371a859","tid":1732210,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pkpkpkpk_7BvDb_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpkpkpkpk_7BvDb_1200x0.png&h=96e889b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滕錦光<br />\n<br />\n警方凌晨 5 時許攻入理大校園，拘捕多人後撤退，理大校長滕錦光之後透過公關向傳媒發放片段，指滕錦光曾希望到現場和學生交流，但警方認為危險不適合，所以他錄製片段。<br />\n<br />\n滕錦光在片段中指，自昨日下午一直和警方溝通，獲警方承諾若示威者不主動攻擊，警方會暫緩攻勢，警方亦容許校內人士和平離開校園，膝錦光會陪同前往警署，確保他們的個案獲公平處理，希望示威者接受建議，和平離開校園。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理大校長滕錦光　聯同浸大、科大、港大、城大校長 籲各方克制盡快離開</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/u-15_QYrHI_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fu-15_QYrHI_1200x0.png&h=b3448823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理工大學示威者和警方對峙持續，警方已全面封鎖理工大學一帶，並警告有可能使用實彈清場；理工大學校長滕錦光，凌晨聯同浸大校長錢大康、城大校長郭位、科大校長史維和港大校長張翔，凌晨發出呼籲，希望在理大一帶的各方克制，學生、校友及其他人盡快離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%95%E9%8C%A6%E5%85%89-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7-%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25BB%2595%25E9%258C%25A6%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%2F&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVh8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=78f9b9aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25BB%2595%25E9%258C%25A6%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%2F&h=12613818\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%95%E9%8C%A6%E5%85%89-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7-%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"d18460d65a06be4a32dae2ae22dc6c4a65358e47","tid":1732210,"uid":49998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"讀左咁耐先知佢個樣生成咁<br />\n咁撚樣衰"},{"pid":"a7643fb0a18df76088bd4a7e5552b1bc99949816","tid":1732210,"uid":36420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16c92e4d63ecb40edf579b53a93850cd636ef70b","tid":1732210,"uid":307189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"全面封鎖又點樣盡快離開呀"},{"pid":"b3ff0cceac926aa137167e7b4378c23a82417052","tid":1732210,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:50:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自盡啦垃圾"}]}